 ('137', '155', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Rovr:</strong>&nbsp;Cross Platform Mobile & Tablet Point of Sales</p>', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', '2017-11-07 00:17:31', '2017-11-07 13:33:36', '6e8034b1-5344-41ab-88ca-d631bb575c64'),
 ('138', '157', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Rovr is part of the bigger Flexischools platform - a sophisticated solution that allows students to pay for things like food and uniforms using an online account or their student ID. It means schools don’t have to outlay a huge cost in providing each student with a new payment card and can simply use what they already have in place. Simple and smart.</p>\r\n<p>Rovr itself is a hybrid (tablet/mobile) cross platform (android/ios)&nbsp;Point of Sales app built from the ground up to work within this ecosystem.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>My Role:</strong>&nbsp;UX Designer & Code Monkey<br></p>\r\n<ul><li>Requirements capture</li><li>Stakeholder interviews</li><li>Wireframing</li><li>Prototyping</li><li>Technology stack recommendations</li><li>Final design assets and dev handover</li><li>Worked side by side dev team: CSS & HTML</li><li>UI tweaks based on user recordings</li></ul>', NULL, '0', '0', 'intro', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', '2017-11-07 00:17:31', '2017-11-07 13:33:36', 'fc78cd4c-364a-4d36-93fa-9153cfec3647'),
