 ('165', '185', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The team at Lantern dreamt up a payment platform that would make transactions relating to schemes like the National Disability Insurance Scheme frictionless. Traditionally claims are made via snail-mail ensuring long waiting times for entitlements, piles of paperwork and reliance on admin heavy invoice payment systems; ultimately making the delivery of much needed care simpler for providers, carers and people with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p><strong>My Role:</strong> UX designer</p>\r\n<ul><li>Requirements capture</li><li>Stakeholder interviews</li><li>User journeys</li><li>Information architecture&nbsp;</li><li>Wireframing</li><li>Low & high fidelity prototyping</li><li>Final designs for dev handover</li><li>Styleguide documentation</li></ul>\r\n<p><br></p>', NULL, '0', '0', 'intro', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', '2017-11-07 04:13:05', '2017-11-08 00:56:28', 'bd5b7c04-c0f1-4fbe-9851-0fc1307b433a'),
