 ('184', '205', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Hi, I\'m Leah. </strong>I\'ve been hacking away at the web since early 2000. I started out as a graphic designer doing print work, migrated across to web design, then got really interested in what could be done with code. We now have access to amazing technologies that allow us to think up the future and that really excites me.</p>\r\n<p>With so many options now available, I think about these simple quotes a lot:</p>\r\n<p><strong>“Make something people want”</strong><br>&mdash; Paul Graham</p>\r\n<p><strong>“A beautiful product that doesn’t work very well is ugly”</strong><br>&mdash; Jony Ive</p><p>Have a project in mind? <a href=\"mailto:hello@leah.today\">Email me.</a></p>', NULL, '0', '0', 'intro', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', '2017-11-08 01:50:40', '2017-11-08 01:54:26', 'd01695f0-bca8-4111-ad5c-66783d2bbb42');
