96\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"gallery\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"0\",\"fields\":{\"images\":{\"0\":\"97\",\"focus-attr\":[{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"}]}}},\"63\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"0\",\"fields\":{\"highlight\":\"\",\"cssClasses\":\"\",\"paragraph\":\"<p><strong>Teacher insights:<\\/strong>\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>It\'s expensive and hard to attract clientele as a solo operator so being employed by one or many yoga studios is the realistic option for most.<\\/li><li>Generally teach at 3 or more locations, making scheduling a challenge.<\\/li><li>Median teacher salary in Australia $30.84 per hour.<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><strong>Student insights:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>\\\"I find most studios and classes extremely intimidating.\\\"&nbsp;<em>Teachers should be notified of new students so special attention can be paid.<\\/em><\\/li><li>\\\"I\'ve been to a few classes here and then, but it\'s been a bit meh\\\".&nbsp;<em>Bad teacher or wrong type of class: fixed with reviews and better filtering?<\\/em><\\/li><li>\\\"That\'s something girls do. Not for me.\\\"&nbsp;<em>Maybe we should encourage teachers to tailor specific classes to be more inclusive or appealing to certain groups. Can marketing help?<\\/em><\\/li><li>\\\"Yoga class can feel like a lonely place - you go, sweat for a bit and then that\'s it. I\'m too nervous to ask questions\\\".&nbsp;<em>How do we create a sense of community inside and outside of the classroom?&nbsp;<\\/em><\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Job stories<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>User flows . sitemap\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Armed with plenty of insights, we now had our project scope. At the core, Flow should be a mobile & desktop app bringing together yoga teachers and their students, with a strong emphasis on user reviews with many filtering options to find the perfect match. To attract the best teachers to the platform, we should incentivise teachers to ditch their yoga studio job and run their small business from their pocket.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Wireframes<\\/h2>\"}},\"64\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"0\",\"fields\":{\"highlight\":\"\",\"cssClasses\":\"\",\"paragraph\":\"<h2>Mockups<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>High fidelity mockups.<br>Prototypes<\\/p>\"}},\"65\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"gallery\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"0\",\"fields\":{\"images\":{\"0\":\"92\",\"1\":\"91\",\"2\":\"93\",\"3\":\"90\",\"4\":\"89\",\"focus-attr\":[{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"},{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"},{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"},{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"},{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"}]}}}}}}', '2017-10-26 11:18:59', '2017-10-26 11:18:59', '8c6deb93-9b7a-4765-9e9d-c2aa7e82580a'),
