hts, we now had our project scope. To further refine, <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/blog.intercom.com\\/using-job-stories-design-features-ui-ux\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">Job Stories<\\/a> were created for a single source of truth and to reveal anything missed. This brings us to a (long) elevator pitch:<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>At the core, Flow should be a mobile & desktop app bringing together yoga teachers and students, with a strong emphasis on becoming THE destination for yoga classes and teacher reviews. Reviews are everything.<\\/li><li>Give users the option to filter by multiple fields so they can really narrow down their search to find the perfect match.&nbsp;<\\/li><li>Let\'s add the ability to book a class - it\'s the perfect revenue stream and easy to implement with a service like <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/stripe.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">Stripe<\\/a>. It\'s an easy revenue win for both teachers and Flow, and makes student\'s lives easier - who carries around cash these days?<\\/li><li>Make it a mobile app: teachers can keep track of class numbers and revenue. Students can be notified when a class is about to start, or to re-engage those that have lost interest. Aim should be a hybrid approach: responsive website for desktop and mobile (good for SEO), direct users to&nbsp;native apps&nbsp;on android + iOS (react\\/angular)&nbsp;for a better experience.<\\/li><li>Provide a direct line of communication from student to teacher outside of the classroom. Encourage teachers to share insights and resources to further student engagement.<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>There are other factors to consider as well:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>Beyond making it super simple & fast, how do we get yoga teachers to join and list their classes.<\\/li><li>What about yoga studios? How do we include them into the picture.<\\/li><li>How does roll out happen - per city, per country... another metric?<\\/li><li>How is success measured and what are attainable targets to attract future investment?<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"99\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"gallery\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"0\",\"fields\":{\"highlight\":\"1\",\"css\":\"\"}},\"115\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"images\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"fullWidth\":\"\",\"headline\":\"\",\"images\":{\"0\":\"114\",\"1\":\"113\",\"focus-attr\":[{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"},{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"}]}}},\"112\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"images\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"fullWidth\":\"\",\"headline\":\"\",\"images\":{\"0\":\"110\",\"1\":\"111\",\"focus-attr\":[{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"},{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"}]}}},\"107\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"images\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"fullWidth\":\"\",\"headline\":\"\",\"images\":{\"0\":\"109\",\"1\":\"108\",\"focus-attr\":[{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"},{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"}]}}},\"106\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"images\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"fullWidth\":\"\",\"headline\":\"\",\"images\":{\"0\":\"104\",\"focus-attr\":[{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"}]}}}}}}', '2017-10-31 05:22:14', '2017-10-31 05:22:14', '5518e4af-dcf5-4ea4-a65e-69a93734b454'),
