ays?<\\/li><li>Make it a mobile app: teachers can keep track of class numbers and revenue. Students can be notified when a class is about to start, or to re-engage those that have lost interest. Aim should be a hybrid approach: responsive website for desktop and mobile (good for SEO), direct users to&nbsp;native apps&nbsp;on android + iOS (react\\/angular)&nbsp;for a better experience.<\\/li><li>Provide a direct line of communication from student to teacher outside of the classroom. Encourage teachers to share insights and resources to further student engagement.<\\/li><\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>There are other factors to consider as well:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul><li>Beyond making it super simple & fast, how do we get yoga teachers to join and list their classes.<\\/li><li>What about yoga studios? How do we include them into the picture.<\\/li><li>How does roll out happen - per city, per country... another metric?<\\/li><li>How is success measured and what are attainable targets to attract future investment?<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}},\"99\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"gallery\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"0\",\"fields\":{\"highlight\":\"1\",\"cssId\":\"gallery\",\"cssClasses\":\"\",\"cssStyles\":\"background-image: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, right bottom, from(#0f64d4), color-stop(43.7%, #10a7fd), to(#0fd1ab));\\r\\nbackground-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0f64d4 0%, #10a7fd 43.7%, #0fd1ab 100%);\"}},\"117\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"images\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"fullWidth\":\"\",\"headline\":\"\",\"images\":{\"0\":\"98\",\"focus-attr\":[{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"}]}}},\"115\":{\"modified\":\"1\",\"type\":\"images\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"collapsed\":\"0\",\"level\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"fullWidth\":\"\",\"headline\":\"\",\"images\":{\"0\":\"114\",\"1\":\"113\",\"focus-attr\":[{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\":\"0.00\"},{\"data-focus-x\":\"0.00\",\"data-focus-y\"