 ('63', 'field', '29', 'en_us', ' teacher insights it s expensive and hard to attract clientele as a solo operator so being employed by one or many yoga studios is the most realistic option generally teach at 3 or more locations making scheduling a challenge median teacher salary in australia $30 84 per hour student insights i find most studios and classes extremely intimidating teachers should be notified of new students so special attention can be paid i ve been to a few classes here and then but it s been a bit meh bad teacher or wrong type of class fixed with reviews and better filtering that s something girls do not for me maybe we should encourage teachers to tailor specific classes to be more inclusive or appealing to certain groups what role does marketing play yoga class can feel like a lonely place you go sweat for a bit and then that s it i m too nervous to ask questions how do we create a sense of community inside and outside of the classroom i always forget to bring cash with me so i have to rush to the atm before a class add online bookings simple armed with plenty of insights we now had our project scope to further refine job stories were created for a single source of truth and to reveal anything missed this brings us to a long elevator pitch at the core flow should be a mobile desktop app bringing together yoga teachers and students with a strong emphasis on becoming the destination for yoga classes and teacher reviews reviews are everything give users the option to filter by multiple fields so they can really narrow down their search to find the perfect match let s add the ability to book a class it s the perfect revenue stream and easy to implement with a service like stripe it s an easy revenue win for both teachers and flow and makes student s lives easier who carries around cash these days make it a mobile app teachers can keep track of class numbers and revenue students can be notified when a class is about to start or to re engage those that have lost interest aim should be a hybrid approach responsive website for desktop and mobile good for seo direct users to native apps on android ios react angular for a better experience provide a direct line of communication from student to teacher outside of the classroom encourage teachers to share insights and resources to further student engagement there are other factors to consider as well beyond making it super simple fast how do we get yoga teachers to join and list their classes what about yoga studios how do we include them into the picture how does roll out happen per city per country another metric how is success measured and what are attainable targets to attract future investment '),
